CT,20,T
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1778512269
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tue 26 May to Tue 9 Jun
OL,6,FPatterns which bring more settled
OL,7,Fweather are more likely to dominate
OL,8,Ftowards the end of May. Whilst further
OL,9,Frain and showers are possible at
OL,10,Ftimes, there is likely to be longer
OL,11,Fspells of fine and dry weather.
OL,12,FTemperatures are most likely to
OL,13,Frecover close to average, perhaps
OL,14,Fbecoming warm at times. Into June,
OL,15,Fmore mixed conditions are likely with
OL,16,Fspells of rain and showers, but also
OL,17,Fsome drier weather at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
